  "detailed_description": "<br><i>This game was inspired by \"Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy\"</i><br>If you hated that, you'll hate this one too :)<br><br>Play as Willy, a small boy with a lot of crap to give. <br>Willy's cat died so the only logical action is to go get the cat back from heaven. <br><br>By using poo to fling Willy. you climb your way along the unforgiving and difficult path to heaven. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1333890/extras/9736a3265b2ddf724714b6ef11aa0d91.poster.avif?t=1683486964\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1333890/extras/9736a3265b2ddf724714b6ef11aa0d91.webm?t=1683486964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1333890/extras/9736a3265b2ddf724714b6ef11aa0d91.mp4?t=1683486964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Easy to learn but hard to master climbing mechanic using only your gut. <br></li><li> A narration voice to remind you of your failures, hardships, and progress. <br></li><li> A heartwarming and humorous story with cutscenes that you get to explore as you climb.<br></li><li> About 1-5 hrs of gameplay depending on your skill level<br></li><li> No checkpoints, who needs them anyway. (it does save your position, so you can quit and return)<br></li><li> Lots of poop.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1333890/extras/17fc9833536df68ca32633bb7f90c614.poster.avif?t=1683486964\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1333890/extras/17fc9833536df68ca32633bb7f90c614.webm?t=1683486964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1333890/extras/17fc9833536df68ca32633bb7f90c614.mp4?t=1683486964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
